recommend check-in on the newly-discovered systemic gap: whether tools/fixtures/two_rooms_doorway_scan_one.sh's own accepted-word regex should widen to match this tree's actual prevailing Status-line vocabulary, or the ~25 external-research/ documents should each gain the literal word -- a real design call, not mine to make. The two fixes landed this turn are real, verified, and complete; the third discovery is honestly sized and handed forward, not attempted.
